::Killfest::

Killfest nods. "Excellent job. Now we simply massacurre them. The 
defences are firing?"

He frowns as DrillBit asks Starscream to kill Quickstrike. "Don't 
bother, I'll do it. Step back."

He aims his wrists at Quickstrike, four large beam guns emerging from 
them. They glow for a second, firing four beams at Quickstrike. The 
weapon was set on low-energy, but would nonetheless produce an 
explosion the size of Quickstrike.
